		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Louisville Ky</placeName> <date>17<lb/>10</date>&#8212;</p>
				<p>Rev<hi rend="sup">d</hi> and Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Your kind favor is<lb/> duly received.  <persName>Luria</persName> has left us&#44;<lb/> and I hope for &#34;age&#34;.  <persName>Wise</persName> is here&#44;<lb/> with a large lot of <add>Hebrew</add>.  He gains<lb/> much on the ignorant &#40;the majority&#41;<lb/> by his soft <add>&#63;</add>.  He deigns not<lb/> to come near us&#44; &#34;a handful of low<lb/> <add>Hebrew</add>&#34;&#58; but sorry am I to add that with<lb/> very few exceptions they are all his<lb/> admirers.  I am too poor to do much&#59;<lb/> my Sabbath School was <sic>superceded</sic><lb/> by the &#34;<persName>Gerstle</persName>&#34; ordering all the children<lb/> of their School to attend the <add>Hebrew</add> every<lb/> <date>sabbath</date>.  Some go&#44; some stay away<lb/> and others go to Dancing School.<lb/>  Religion is cast aside.  Many<lb/> of the Ashkenazim would join us if<lb/> we would change our <add>Hebrew</add> from <add>Hebrew</add> to<lb/> <add>Hebrew</add>&#44; but &#34;non possunt&#34;&#8212;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Please insert the<lb/> <sic>accompaning</sic> in the Advertising<lb/> Sheet for <date>November</date>.  I hope the</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>enclosed will pay for it.<lb/>  Resp<hi rend="sup">y</hi> &#38; truly Yours</p>
				<p><persName role="author">A. I. H. Bernal</persName></p>
		</body>
